    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/0b0a25a51cb129f4b4f03d4b27357184.avif?t=1760377877\" width=331 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and fight your way trough a giant castle filled with all kinds of monsters. Find new gear, learn new skills and level up to better your chances against evil. ALARIC is a blend of classic boomershooters and traditional metroidvanias.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/bbe32adb42562dcc38c0afd601279f93.poster.avif?t=1760377877\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/bbe32adb42562dcc38c0afd601279f93.webm?t=1760377877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/36c762906042efdeb870d713fcc36ef7.avif?t=1760377877\" width=331 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy some custom heavy metal music mixed with some medieval elements. The music will change and intensify based on what's going on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/38dc1d2f2601f1654553608317cf8b92.poster.avif?t=1760377877\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/38dc1d2f2601f1654553608317cf8b92.webm?t=1760377877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/a1b700cad132ec9fdc5f15e4591f540e.avif?t=1760377877\" width=331 height=84 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a giant castle and uncover the dark history of this place. Gain new powerups and find new ways to traverse the map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/db52e51c30ea4330e3790e405b7b89e9.poster.avif?t=1760377877\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3121810/extras/db52e51c30ea4330e3790e405b7b89e9.webm?t=1760377877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for danger.</p>",
